flowRoot.flowPara: New to GNOME? Learn how to get around. Browse the web, connect to your online accounts, learn how to manage your windows and workspaces, switch tasks and respond to messages.

3.16 is the latest GNOME release, and the result of six months' work by the GNOME project. It includes new features and a large number of smaller improvements and enhancements. The release contains 28859 changes by approximately 871 contributors. Read all about the new features and improvements of the 3.16 release.
